all industrials index fell 3.2 points to 3,681.5, led by a slump
in bank stocks.
</P>
<P>
National Australia Bank finished 17.7 cents down and Westpac
bank shed 23.7 cents on top turnover of 17.82 million shares.
</P>
<P>
The insurance sector finished 32.7 points higher on 5,448.3,
with National Mutual gaining one cent.
</P>
<P>
National turnover totalled 273.3 million shares valued at
786.63 million Australian dollars (617.5 million US dollars).
</P>
