<TEXT>
<P>
SOFIA, April 1 (Xinhua) -- Bulgarian geologists have discovered
a gold deposit in mountains in central and southern of Bulgaria,
geological professor Todor Marinov, the chairman of the geology
and mineral resources ministry said.
</P>
<P>
The gold deposits at Panagyurishte, 60 kilometers east of
