structure around Angola in time, saying the move would strengthen
people's belief in peace and create conditions for the free
movement of people and goods in the country.
</P>
<P>
The Angolan government should be active in creating conditions
for UNITA and other opposition parties to operate countrywide
without limitation, the communique said.
</P>
<P>
Only with such conditions, next talks between Angolan
President Eduardo dos Santos and Savimbi might be successful, the
communique added. enditem

